1. "Ona je izabrala knjigu *kojom* se bavi istraživanjem." (She chose the book with which she is doing research.)
2. "Kojom brzinom se kreće?" (What speed is it moving at?)
3. "Ona je izabrala putanju *kojom* će se kretati." (She chose the path which she will follow.)
4. "Kojom rukom pisanje?" (With which hand do you write?)
5. "Ona je izabrala pravac *kojom* će ići." (She chose the direction which she will take.)